Amy Okonkwo (amuru 26 August 1996) bu onye egwuregwu basketball nke Naijiria na-agbara ndị Mahadum Texas Christian na ndi Nigerian National Team.
Ọ nwetara ọkpụkpọ oku mbụ ya maka ndị otu egwuregwu bọọlụ Naịjirịa na 2021
Amy Okonkwo bụkwa onye otu egwuregwu basketball ụmụ nwanyị nke Nigeria, D'tigress, na Tokyo Olympic 2020 na Japan
Amy bụ onye kacha mee nke ọma na ndị otu egwuregwu na Japan site n'inweta akara iri na anọ n'egwuregwu ahu
